参考:  <a href="http://stackoverflow.com/questions/1560572/ruby-delete-multiple-hash-keys" target="_blank"> http://stackoverflow.com/questions/1560572/ruby-delete-multiple-hash-keys </a>

<pre>sg552@youku:/sg552/workspace/postman$ bundle exec rails c
Loading development environment (Rails 3.2.9)
&gt;&gt; apple = {:shape =&gt; 'ball', :taste =&gt; 'sweet', :color =&gt; 'red' }
=&gt; {:shape=&gt;"ball", :taste=&gt;"sweet", :color=&gt;"red"}

&gt;&gt; apple.except(:shape, :color)
=&gt; {:taste=&gt;"sweet"}
</pre>

<p>结论： ActiveSupport 需要我们挖掘的东西太多了， 有空时务必看一下  (  we need to keep learning ActiveSupport )</p>
